<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>A Deployment is broken and in need of assistance</h1>
    <p>
      <%= @from.given_name %>, has reported a problem with a Deployment request for <%= @deployment.full_name %> on Stratus at <%= Time.now.to_s(:pretty) %>. 
    </p>
    <p>
      To read about this Deployment, just follow this link: <%= link_to @deployment_show_url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for using Stratus and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
